  "instructions": [
    "Marinate the red snapper fillets in a mixture of lime juice, honey, garlic, cumin, red pepper flakes, salt, and black pepper for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the marinated red snapper onto skewers, leaving space between each piece.",
    "Drizzle the citrus glaze over the snapper and brush to coat.",
    "Grill the anticuchos for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the coconut oil in a small pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the red onion to the pan and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until slightly caramelized.",
    "Stir in the fresh cilantro and ginger.",
    "Serve the grilled snapper with the toasted onion and cilantro mixture.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro, if desired."
  ],
